{{zh-hanzi|[[一]][[家]][[大小]]}}
==Mandarin==
===Etymology===
Literally: one house, big and small

===Idiom===
{{cmn-idiom|ts|pin=yī jiā dàxiǎo|pint=yi1jia1da4xiao3|rs=一00}}
# the whole family
#: [[Simplified Chinese|s]] [[放假]][[了]]，[[我们]]'''一家大小'''[[往]][[乡下]][[去]][[探望]][[祖母]]。 
#: [[Traditional Chinese|t]] [[放假]][[了]]，[[我們]]'''一家大小'''[[往]][[鄉下]][[去]][[探望]][[祖母]]。
#: ''We had a holiday, so our '''whole family''' went to the countryside to visit grandmother.''

